300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wilson_volleyball_castaway_front.jpg?fit=1001%2C1000&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 31942, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2022/01/18/roll-of-the-dice-hunter-of-invisible-game/", "url_meta": {"origin": 9730, "position": 2}, "title": "Roll of the Dice: Hunter of Invisible Game", "author": "Ken", "date": "January 18, 2022", "format": false, "excerpt": "It's one of Bruce's most audacious songs ever, a ten-minute, waltz-time, post-apocalyptic allegory for the decline of civilization.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Roll of the Dice&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Roll of the Dice", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/roll-of-the-dice/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/hunter.jpg?fit=680%2C879&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/hunter.jpg?fit=680%2C879&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/hunter.jpg?fit=680%2C879&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 61151, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/10/18/kingdom-of-days-october-18-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 9730, "position": 3}, "title": "Kingdom of Days: October 18", "author": "Ken", "date": "October 18, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "Bruce broke up the band on this date in 1989, but there are plenty of happy highlights too: the first-ever performances of \"Drive All Night\" and \"Hungry Heart,\" an adorable tape-recorded message to local schoolchildren, the premiere of Legends of Springsteen, Charlie's first E Street appearance, and more.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https: